<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - Kebaktian Anak</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;

            background-image: url('/images/background-image.png');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-repeat: no-repeat;
            background-attachment: fixed;
        }

        .container {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 20px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            max-width: 1000px;
        }

        .left-section, .right-section {
            padding: 30px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
            width: fit-content; /* Container mengikuti ukuran konten */
        }

        .left-section:hover, .right-section:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        h3 {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 24px;
            color: #007bff;
        }

        p {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #007bff, #0056b3);
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: background 0.3s ease, transform 0.3s ease;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0056b3, #003d80);
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .container {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center; /* Pusatkan container di mobile */
            }

            .left-section, .right-section {
                width: 100%; /* Lebar penuh di mobile */
                max-width: 400px; /* Batasi lebar maksimum di mobile */
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <main class="container">
        <div class="left-section">
            <h3>Gedung Hastinapura</h3>
            <p>Para pendamping dapat mendaftarkan anak-anaknya melalui tautan ini.</p>
            <p>Khusus untuk pendamping anak-anak yang sudah dipilih.</p>
            <p>Tidak ada orang tua yang mendaftar di sini.</p>
            <p><strong>Catatan: Anak yang sudah masuk sebagai peserta Paduan Suara dan Hari Anak, tidak perlu mendaftarÂ ulang.</strong></p>
            <a href="/booking/hastina" class="btn">Daftar</a>
        </div>
        <div class="right-section">
            <h3>Gedung Yudistira</h3>
            <p>Para orang tua yang mendampingi anaknya bisa melalui tautan ini.</p>
            <a href="/booking/yudistira" class="btn">Daftar</a>
        </div>
    </main>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

    <script>
        document.querySelectorAll('.btn').forEach(button => {
            button.addEventListener('click', (event) => {
                event.preventDefault();
                setTimeout(() => {
                    window.location.href = event.target.href;
                }, 500); // Redirect setelah 500ms (opsional)
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>
